flowchart TD
A[Incoming Call] --> B["Greeting: Thank you for calling Pop A Lock. How can I help you today?"]
B --> C[Capture caller id and callback number, repeat callback]
C --> D[Get caller name and role]
D --> E[Collect business name]
E --> F[Collect service address]
F --> G[Double click sub area]
G --> H["Click magnifying glass<br/>Verify address and assign zone"]

H --> I["Ask: are you authorized to approve this work?"]
I --> J[Collect job details and number of doors]
J --> K[Ask urgency]
K --> L[Do not quote pricing]
L --> M["Tell customer: commercial locksmith will review and call back"]
M --> N["Inform: proof of authorization required at service"]
N --> O[Repeat full summary]
O --> P["Ask: how did you hear about us?"]
P --> Q[Add call]
Q --> R[Leave lead status as NONE]
R --> S[Do not assign]
S --> T[Do not schedule]
T --> U[End call]
